639
00:57:40,589 --> 00:57:44,468
* HOLD MY MOTHER, TOLD ME *

640
00:57:44,636 --> 00:57:47,889
* WAY-O-WAY *

641
00:57:50,767 --> 00:57:54,563
* WE ON OUR WAY, JOE *

642
00:57:55,022 --> 00:57:58,401
* I FIRST MET A YANKEE GIRL *

643
00:57:58,902 --> 00:58:02,572
